### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Create insurance for a car (using ORIGINAL DTO property names)
POST {{baseUrl}}/insurance
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carId": "5",
  "insuranceProvider": "State Farm",
  "policyNumber": "SF123456789",
  "startDate": "2024-01-01",
  "endDate": "2025-01-01"
}

### 2. Create another insurance
POST {{baseUrl}}/insurance
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carId": "2",
  "insuranceProvider": "Geico",
  "policyNumber": "GC987654321",
  "startDate": "2024-02-01",
  "endDate": "2025-02-01"
}

### 3. Get all insurance records
GET {{baseUrl}}/insurance

### 4. Get insurance by ID (replace {id} with actual insurance ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/insurance/1

### 5. Get insurance by car ID (replace {carId} with actual car ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/insurance/car/1

### 6. Update insurance (replace {id} with actual insurance ID)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/insurance/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "insuranceProvider": "State Farm Updated",
  "policyNumber": "SF-UPDATED-123",
  "endDate": "2025-06-01"
}

### 7. Check if insurance is valid for car (replace {carId})
GET {{baseUrl}}/insurance/car/1/valid

### 8. Get expiring insurances (within 30 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/insurance/expiring?days=30

### 9. Delete insurance (replace {id})
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/insurance/1